# Normalize all text files to LF in the repository. This project is edited on
# Windows but built and run on Linux (Docker/Alpine), so committing CRLF would
# break shell scripts and produce noisy cross-platform diffs. Git still checks
# files out with native endings locally where relevant.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets — never touch these.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.webp binary
*.gif binary
*.ttf binary
*.zip binary
*.pdf binary
